@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title From source to deployable script

start
:Write validator(s) in validators/;
:aiken check
(type-check + run tests);
if (green?) then (no)
  :fix code / tests;
  detach
else (yes)
endif
:aiken build;
:plutus.json blueprint (CIP-57)
generated;
if (validator takes\ncompile-time parameters?) then (yes)
  :aiken blueprint apply
(bake in each parameter);
else (no)
endif
fork
  :aiken blueprint address
(spend -> script address);
fork again
  :aiken blueprint policy
(mint -> policy id);
end fork
:off-chain app reads plutus.json
(Lucid / Mesh / PyCardano);
:build & submit transactions
the validator will approve;
stop
@enduml
